Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency alert for all Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please head for the shelter right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-There are no guards around.\N-Emergency to all Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-They must have known we were back.\N-Please head for the shelter right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They are distances away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like an ambush,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but something is amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They might have other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way out is to confront them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head for the OSF headquarters in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be purged from this land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the New Himuka government!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create a relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here and between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller\Ncoaster inside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and the unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s the same today\NTo connect vividly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,NAGI'S ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, there is no need\Nfor us to fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find a way to break the brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you daydreaming or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun is just about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and extract your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, won't you listen to my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Such power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have gone through\Nsome power amplification treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have to fight? Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate fighting, then just stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head will be mine soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hand over your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had always wanted to join the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was never scouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I enrolled in the training school\Nbecause I didn't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I was from the royal family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone treated me differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were on breaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we went to our secret base
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I only made it into OSF
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because you were there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to save yours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just die already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be saved after you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will only find happiness in your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and even finish the mission New Himuka gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.\NStop moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you damaged your precious brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that I sever it now from your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our secret training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me about this great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and become popular with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to be actively involved\Nlike Major General Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You liked to fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you weren't taking it seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't have made it through OSF training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the better performance and skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Die for New Himuka's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always needed your help\Nbefore the theory test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You were popular among the girls of our peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But why was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's Nagi's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep using your brain power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you and take your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not order me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice ordering me to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want it.\NI didn't want to fight you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was so scared.\NI couldn't fight it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it turn into this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it into the OSF,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we finally became part of the Seto Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could keep messing around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe him my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had always imagined that I would die fighting\Nthe Others gallantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, I'd become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But at some point, everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm dying either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I felt insecure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you told me I should focus on\Nbecoming a great soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to save the people.\NBut I couldn't even save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish this journey for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time to mourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, how is the preparation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complete. You can begin anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your voices down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This can be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For Nagi's sake, I can't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was set that way\Nso people would avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi is the only person inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to discuss Seiran's operations\Nwith Suoh's executives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, I have questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who ordered Nagi to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That worthless fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We already gave him enough amplifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was just another\Nordinary brain power user.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are you doing this, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The power you possess
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ability to manipulate gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We need that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even Suoh has learned about Yuito's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would turn yourself in quietly\Nif I sent your friend to do the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just listened to the government's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,this wouldn't even be necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were branded as a traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have come to me for help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have always been so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You make your own decision and listen to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have the resolve to be a member\Nof the Sumeragi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why Father never wanted you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the duty of our family is to fulfill\NYakumo Sumeragi's legacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi's legacy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said enough. You do not need to know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this related to the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi was one of the first\Nto move from Moon to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned something\Nyou shouldn't in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. I want to have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu wants to sacrifice the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore Togetsu and their wild goose chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they brainwash you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the one who got brainwashed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After we learned of that information at Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we concluded it was highly possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not understand\NYakumo Sumeragi's grand vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Yakumo Sumeragi's grand vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know by now, the Extinction Belt\Nwas created by the people on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give you a picture of\Nhow ridiculous those people can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After Yakumo Sumeragi built this country,\Nhe has decided that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,even if he couldn't witness the feat himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the Extinction Belt must be neutralized\Nthe Moon will be retaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We inherited the legacy from Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have our revenge on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo's wish was to have revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Following the will of our founding father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,member of the Sumeragi family\Nmust fulfill their duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the very purpose of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your power to move the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When the path to the Moon is cleared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall have our revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving the Extinction Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible with every brain\Nin our country via SAS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they are just commoners,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,linking thousands of them together
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,will give us enough power for the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By linking more brain power users,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka's military might\Nwill reach a whole new level!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even users like us can't handle\Nthe load from SAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need is their brains and body parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The people are not your property.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, don't you find it absurd\Nto have revenge on people from 2000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yakumo Sumeragi's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bringing that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He is long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in his slumber deep under Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is waiting for the moment\Nto have his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the cold sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the Sumeragi family,\Nyou must understand its magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The tradition from 2000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or my identity as a Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find the truth with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will decide the course of action\Nafter I've witnessed the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be banished from our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,without being a Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Violence is the option to make you obey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hoped that you'd listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems impossible now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I won't let you arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Father\Nwould be disappointed in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also believe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to fight our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded the whole conversation you had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with Chief Sumeragi in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hacked into the administration system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. It wasn't easy by any means,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did it for the first and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki's previous plan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,might have use of this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send the message to every citizen\Nvia Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Arahabaki's password.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a terminal device that\Nonly shows the password once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't fall so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can broadcast the footage nationwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But by doing so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I respect your decision as our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to face any consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a team after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But we all share Geman's resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if it's right to destroy\Nthe very thing my brother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I feel so lost right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know his motive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So action must be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head to Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tell the people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret New Himuka and my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can leave the work in Suoh to Yuito's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get working too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can you persuade the leaders of Seiran?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We could try talking to Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he even listen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to try to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are movements at the\NSupernatural Life Research Facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who turned into Others\Nare being transported away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I checked the transportation record.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of it\Nis Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,NAOMI AND ALICE
